00:28:15.098 --> 00:28:19.490
with the hideous roar of their
howlings and their screamings

00:28:19.490 --> 00:28:22.170
and they tear him limb from
limb.

00:28:22.170 --> 00:28:27.475
The chaste poet was unable to
pass uninjured in that wild

00:28:27.475 --> 00:28:31.570
surrounding waste.
