00:28:49.734 --> 00:28:53.700
because he had the power to do
something with his poetry.

00:28:53.700 --> 00:28:56.490
His verse actually had a
physical impact on the world.

00:28:56.490 --> 00:29:00.823
The rocks, the woods,
and the trees danced in

00:29:00.823 --> 00:29:05.563
response to Orpheus' music.
In Comus, the

00:29:05.563 --> 00:29:09.888
